<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>키워드로 장소검색하고 목록으로 표출하기</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/map.css" />
    <style>
        body {
            background-image: url("/img/realback.jpg");
            background-size: cover;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="section services-section">
    <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-12 pl-md-5" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
                    <h2 class="mb-4" style="text-align:center">직거래 이동시간확인하기</h2>
                    <h4 class="mb-4" style="text-align:center; color: #2e3133"><a href="/weather">홈 화면 이동</a></h4>
                </div>
            </div>
    </div>
</div> <!-- .section -->

<div class="map_wrap">
    <div id="map" style="margin: 50px auto; width: 1000px; height: 100%; position:relative;overflow:hidden;"></div>
    <div id="menu_wrap" class="bg_white" style="margin-left: 380px;">
        <div class="option">
            <div>
                <form onsubmit="searchPlaces(); return false;">
                    키워드 : <input type="text" value="서울" id="keyword" size="15">
                    <button type="submit">검색하기</button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
        <hr>
        <ul id="placesList"></ul>
        <div id="pagination"></div>
    </div>
</div>
<p style="text-align:center">
    <em>지도를 마우스로 클릭하면 선 그리기가 시작되고<br>오른쪽 마우스를 클릭하면 선 그리기가 종료됩니다</em>
</p>
<script type="text/javascript" src="//dapi.kakao.com/v2/maps/sdk.js?appkey=c7242e06fde35a06152da46f2d1c6690&libraries=services"></script>
<script src="/js/map.js"></script>
</body>
</html>